rComments: A really great prof! His class was by far my favorite this past semester, and he made dry legal material sound as dramatic as a soap opera. This is not an easy A, and you'll have to work very hard to do well. That being said would still 100% recommend.

Ewing made topics seem engaging and relevant. Class discussions were always substantive he always made students feel included. He took into account student abilities in marking and really worked with to improve. Assignment expectations and feedback were somewhat unclear but was always available to clarify in Office Hours. Excellent, caring prof.

Ewing is super passionate about the content and wants students to do well. His enthusiasm is contagious. Very clear about expectations. The grading scheme is very forgiving and he gives a lot of marks just for completion. Bonus: hes still young, so he hasnt been jaded by academic like others in the POL department. Just an excellent professor.
